data.description: Seller is offering $5,000 to buyer at closing to buy down interest rate points or closing fees. Also, a Home Warranty. This move-in ready villa with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms is in the subdivision of Ashton Oaks. Upgrades include granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. NEW REFRIGERATOR AND NEW DISHWASHER. breakfast bar, flat top stove.  The master room has a custom Walk-In closet system. The spacious screened lanai overlooks a spacious backyard great for cookouts. Also, A NEW 2024 ROOF. This community also offers a pool and cabana, great for entertaining family and guests.NO CDD, NEW REFRIGERATOR, NEW DISHWASHER, NEW CARPET THOUGHOUT THE HOME AND NEW 2024 ROOF! Conveniently located near schools, Wiregrass mall, wiregrass outlet. Plenty of medical care in the area. The interstate is just minutes away from Wiregrass Mall. It's a MUST SEE.
